ervermania.com/\" target=\"_blank\">ServerMania</a>&nbsp;has sent in his first LowEndBox offer available in Buffalo New York and Toronto Canada.</p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>VPS-512L</strong><p></p><ul><li>512MB RAM</li><li>1024MB Burst</li><li>30GB RAID10 Diskspace</li><li>1 IPv4 Addresss</li><li>100 Mbps Port Speed</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>1250 GB Bandwidth</li><li>$4/Month \u2013 Coupon Code:&nbsp;<strong>LEB2</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://shp.servermania.com/order/product?p=366\" target=\"_blank\">Order Link</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>VPS-1024L</strong><p></p><ul><li>1024MB RAM</li><li>2048MB Burst</li><li>75GB RAID10 Diskspace</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>100 Mbps Port Speed</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>2000 GB Bandwidth</li><li>$7/Month \u2013 Coupon Code: <strong>LEB3</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://shp.servermania.com/order/product?p=368\" target=\"_blank\">Order Link</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>ServerMania was previously known as B2Net Solutions, under which they were operating for 10 years and have undergone a rebranding. Their IP space is still registered as \u201cB2Net Solutions\u201d at this time and the company&nbsp;is legally registered in Ontario Canada. The billing and order panel looks very nice, different to the default WHMCS that\u2019s seen amongst a number of providers. ServerMania seem to <a href=\"http://www.servermania.com/support-fleet.htm\" title=\"ServerMania Support\" target=\"_blank\">push their support credentials</a> on their website with statements of \u201c30 minute help desk response time guarantee,\u201d a \u201c30 second live chat initial response\u201d and a \u201c60 second phone initial response guarantee\u201d through their 24/7 phone support line (1.888.237.6637). Beyond this they offer a 100% network uptime guarantee and a 100% power uptime guarantee, where some providers offer one or the other. Still with all of this take a read through their <a href=\"http://www.servermania.com/tos.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Terms of Services</a>.<br>\n<span id=\"more-3603\"></span></p><p>Payments are accepted via Credit Card and Paypal, however there is no money back guarantee or refunds offered. You can choose either Buffalo New York or Toronto Canada on signup.</p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 13px;line-height: 19px\">Network Tests</strong><br>\nEach page has a Test IP and a series of Test Files as well as DC information.<br>\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">New York</span>: <a href=\"http://www.servermania.com/newyork-datacenter.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.servermania.com/newyork-datacenter.htm</a><br>\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Toronto</span>: <a href=\"http://www.servermania.com/toronto-datacenter.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.servermania.com/toronto-datacenter.htm</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fservermania-4month-512mb-openvz-vps-in-new-york-usa-toronto-canada%2F&amp;t=ServerMania%20-%20%244%2FMonth%20512MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20Buffalo%20%28NY%29%20USA%20%26%20Toronto%20Canada\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=ServerMania%20-%20%244%2FMonth%20512MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20Buffalo%20%28NY%29%20USA%20%26%20Toronto%20Canada&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fse